## Guardrails
- **No duplicate/thin content**: Unique, valuable content per page
- **Schema.org markup**: Structured data for all scholarship listings
- **Cache + CDN**: Static pages served from edge, <100ms TTFB
- **Zero PII**: Never embed user data in programmatic pages
- **Robots/meta directives**: Respect noindex, canonical URLs

## SEO Best Practices
- Full-site sitemap refresh: Daily at 02:00 EST
- Delta sitemap updates: Hourly for new pages
- IndexNow submission: Immediate after publish
- Canonical URL deduplication
